# Local Worker dev overrides for `wrangler dev` (copy to `.dev.vars`).
#
# Splitwise has NO app-level API credentials — each user's personal Splitwise
# API key arrives through the connector's OAuth login form (served at
# /authorize), not from here. There is nothing required in this file to run the
# hosted connector locally; it exists only as the conventional place for any
# future Worker-only dev override.
